{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01XXV17SXzAQfah4DWSfCwbd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013HVAb8ee711b5udcTWLL7w","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"ls /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/04_*/design.cir 2>/dev/null | head -1 && head -30 /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/04_*/design.cir 2>/dev/null | head -30","description":"Check Block 04 design for PDK reference"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12716,"cache_read_input_tokens":27044,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":12716},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"6b6762c6-da26-4ab2-9948-fabd8350e852"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013HVAb8ee711b5udcTWLL7w","type":"tool_result","content":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/04_current_limiter/design.cir\n* Block 04: Current Limiter (v2)\n* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n*\n* Topology: Sense-mirror brick-wall limiter with Vth-based detection\n*\n*   XMs: Sense PMOS (gate shared with pass device)\n*         W=2u L=0.5u, pass device is 10x W=100u L=0.5u\n*         Geometric ratio N = 1000/2 = 500\n*   XRs: Sense resistor converts Isense to voltage\n*         xhigh_po W=1u L=3.15u → Rs ~ 6182 ohm\n*   XMdet: Detection NMOS (W=5u L=1u), trips when Vsense > Vth (~0.7V)\n*   XRpu: Pull-up keeps det_n at bvdd during normal operation (10.5k)\n*   XMclamp: Clamp PMOS (W=20u L=1u) pulls gate toward bvdd\n*\n* The Vds mismatch between sense device (Vds ~ bvdd) and pass device\n* (Vds ~ bvdd-pvdd) amplifies sense current at high pvdd, giving an\n* effective mirror ratio lower than geometric 500.\n*\n* Measured results:\n*   TT27: 79.0mA, SS150: 135.7mA, FF-40: 43.4mA\n*   PVT spread: 3.1x (136/43.4)\n*   Quiescent: ~0.0002 uA at Iload=0\n*   Short circuit: ~105mA with limiter vs ~598mA without\n*   Loop PM: ~104 deg at UGB=423kHz (with real error amp, break-loop AC)\n*\n.subckt current_limiter gate bvdd pvdd gnd ilim_flag\n\n* === Sense PMOS ===\nXMs  sense_n gate bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=2e-6 l=0.5e-6","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"31f978fe-e761-4c25-b167-60daff1aec24","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:59:40.224Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/04_current_limiter/design.cir\n* Block 04: Current Limiter (v2)\n* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n*\n* Topology: Sense-mirror brick-wall limiter with Vth-based detection\n*\n*   XMs: Sense PMOS (gate shared with pass device)\n*         W=2u L=0.5u, pass device is 10x W=100u L=0.5u\n*         Geometric ratio N = 1000/2 = 500\n*   XRs: Sense resistor converts Isense to voltage\n*         xhigh_po W=1u L=3.15u → Rs ~ 6182 ohm\n*   XMdet: Detection NMOS (W=5u L=1u), trips when Vsense > Vth (~0.7V)\n*   XRpu: Pull-up keeps det_n at bvdd during normal operation (10.5k)\n*   XMclamp: Clamp PMOS (W=20u L=1u) pulls gate toward bvdd\n*\n* The Vds mismatch between sense device (Vds ~ bvdd) and pass device\n* (Vds ~ bvdd-pvdd) amplifies sense current at high pvdd, giving an\n* effective mirror ratio lower than geometric 500.\n*\n* Measured results:\n*   TT27: 79.0mA, SS150: 135.7mA, FF-40: 43.4mA\n*   PVT spread: 3.1x (136/43.4)\n*   Quiescent: ~0.0002 uA at Iload=0\n*   Short circuit: ~105mA with limiter vs ~598mA without\n*   Loop PM: ~104 deg at UGB=423kHz (with real error amp, break-loop AC)\n*\n.subckt current_limiter gate bvdd pvdd gnd ilim_flag\n\n* === Sense PMOS ===\nXMs  sense_n gate bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=2e-6 l=0.5e-6","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
