{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01VwRSTMinS5AffCrVrFdC8h","type":"tool_result","content":"* Sky130 PDK Library for PVDD Regulator\n* Devices: nfet_g5v0d10v5, pfet_g5v0d10v5, cap_mim_m3_1, res_xhigh_po\n* All 5 corners: tt, ss, ff, sf, fs\n\n.param SKY130_SPICE = '/home/ubuntu/.volare/volare/sky130/versions/0fe599b2afb6708d281543108caf8310912f54af/sky130A/libs.ref/sky130_fd_pr/spice'\n\n* ================================================================\n* Parasitic model for poly resistor (simplified — cap to substrate)\n* ================================================================\n.subckt sky130_fd_pr__model__parasitic__res_po r0 r1 sub w=1 l=1\n.param cpoly_area = 1e-16\n.param cp = 'cpoly_area * w * l'\nc0 r0 sub 'cp/2'\nc1 r1 sub 'cp/2'\n.ends sky130_fd_pr__model__parasitic__res_po\n\n* ================================================================\n* TT corner\n* ================================================================\n.lib tt\n\n* --- Global params ---\n.param mc_mm_switch = 0\n* MIM cap\n.param m3_dw = 0\n.param tol_m3 = 0\n.param camimc = 2.0e-15\n.param cpmimc = 3.8e-17\n.param rm3 = 0.047\n.param rcvia3 = 9.3\n.param tc1rm3 = 3.3e-3\n.param tc2rm3 = 0\n.param tc1rvia3 = 0\n.param tc2rvia3 = 0\n* Resistor\n.param sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po__var_mult = 0\n* NFET g5v0d10v5 slope/diff (all 0 for nominal)\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__toxe_slope = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__toxe_slope1 = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__toxe_slope2 = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__toxe_slope3 = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__vth0_slope = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__voff_slope = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__nfactor_slope = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__wlod_diff = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__kvth0_diff = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__lkvth0_diff = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__wkvth0_diff = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__ku0_diff = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__lku0_diff = 0","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"e997ff25-b355-4ecf-b805-5a24cbec18e0","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:59:44.205Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"* Sky130 PDK Library for PVDD Regulator\n* Devices: nfet_g5v0d10v5, pfet_g5v0d10v5, cap_mim_m3_1, res_xhigh_po\n* All 5 corners: tt, ss, ff, sf, fs\n\n.param SKY130_SPICE = '/home/ubuntu/.volare/volare/sky130/versions/0fe599b2afb6708d281543108caf8310912f54af/sky130A/libs.ref/sky130_fd_pr/spice'\n\n* ================================================================\n* Parasitic model for poly resistor (simplified — cap to substrate)\n* ================================================================\n.subckt sky130_fd_pr__model__parasitic__res_po r0 r1 sub w=1 l=1\n.param cpoly_area = 1e-16\n.param cp = 'cpoly_area * w * l'\nc0 r0 sub 'cp/2'\nc1 r1 sub 'cp/2'\n.ends sky130_fd_pr__model__parasitic__res_po\n\n* ================================================================\n* TT corner\n* ================================================================\n.lib tt\n\n* --- Global params ---\n.param mc_mm_switch = 0\n* MIM cap\n.param m3_dw = 0\n.param tol_m3 = 0\n.param camimc = 2.0e-15\n.param cpmimc = 3.8e-17\n.param rm3 = 0.047\n.param rcvia3 = 9.3\n.param tc1rm3 = 3.3e-3\n.param tc2rm3 = 0\n.param tc1rvia3 = 0\n.param tc2rvia3 = 0\n* Resistor\n.param sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po__var_mult = 0\n* NFET g5v0d10v5 slope/diff (all 0 for nominal)\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__toxe_slope = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__toxe_slope1 = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__toxe_slope2 = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__toxe_slope3 = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__vth0_slope = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__voff_slope = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__nfactor_slope = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__wlod_diff = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__kvth0_diff = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__lkvth0_diff = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__wkvth0_diff = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__ku0_diff = 0\n.param sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5__lku0_diff = 0","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
