{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AYcnFKAdRmf9Y6Kaempyms","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* Block 08: Mode Control\n     2→* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n     3→*\n     4→* Architecture: Shared resistor ladder + 4 HV comparators with hysteresis + CMOS logic\n     5→*\n     6→* Resistor ladder: BVDD → Rtop → tap1 → R12 → tap2 → R23 → tap3 → R34 → tap4 → Rbot → GND\n     7→*   tap1 = highest voltage (trips at lowest BVDD = TH1 = 2.5V)\n     8→*   tap4 = lowest voltage (trips at highest BVDD = TH4 = 5.6V)\n     9→*\n    10→* UNITS: MOSFETs use SI (meters), Resistors use µm (per PDK model convention)\n    11→* HV device model valid range: L=20-100µm, W=20-100µm\n    12→*\n    13→.subckt mode_control bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off\n    14→\n    15→* =============================================\n    16→* CONVERGENCE AIDS\n    17→* =============================================\n    18→C_tap1 tap1 gnd 50f\n    19→C_tap2 tap2 gnd 50f\n    20→C_tap3 tap3 gnd 50f\n    21→C_tap4 tap4 gnd 50f\n    22→C_c1o  c1o  gnd 20f\n    23→C_c2o  c2o  gnd 20f\n    24→C_c3o  c3o  gnd 20f\n    25→C_c4o  c4o  gnd 20f\n    26→\n    27→* =============================================\n    28→* RESISTOR LADDER: BVDD to GND (w,l in µm)\n    29→* =============================================\n    30→* Ratios for threshold targets:\n    31→*   TH1=2.5V: (R12+R23+R34+Rbot)/Rtot = 1.226/2.5 = 0.4904\n    32→*   TH2=4.2V: (R23+R34+Rbot)/Rtot     = 1.226/4.2 = 0.29190\n    33→*   TH3=4.5V: (R34+Rbot)/Rtot         = 1.226/4.5 = 0.27244\n    34→*   TH4=5.6V: Rbot/Rtot               = 1.226/5.6 = 0.21893\n    35→*\n    36→.param rtop_l = 241\n    37→.param r12_l  = 94\n    38→.param r23_l  = 9.2\n    39→.param r34_l  = 25\n    40→.param rbot_l = 103\n    41→\n    42→XRtop bvdd tap1 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rtop_l\n    43→XR12  tap1 tap2 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r12_l\n    44