{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VqEMnCdLVTevfsH56Zodkc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01JxJcJkBoGoX2AR4A8ES3t6","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/design.cir","content":"* Block 08: Mode Control\n* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n*\n* Architecture: Shared resistor ladder + 4 PMOS-diffpair comparators + CMOS logic\n* UNITS: MOSFETs = SI (meters), Resistors = µm\n* HV model valid: L=[20,100)µm, W=[20,100)µm\n*\n* Comparator topology:\n*   PMOS diff pair: M_p1 gate=tap (mirror input), M_p2 gate=vref (output)\n*   NMOS mirror load: M_n3 diode on p1 side, M_n4 mirrors to p2 side\n*   When tap > vref: |Vgs_p1| < |Vgs_p2| → I_p1 < I_p2 → c_out rises HIGH\n*   At startup (BVDD≈0): no current → c_out ≈ 0 → comp = 0 (POR state) ✓\n*   Buffer: 2 inverters (non-inverting) → comp = c_out polarity\n*\n.subckt mode_control bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off\n\n* =============================================\n* CONVERGENCE AIDS\n* =============================================\nC_tap1 tap1 gnd 100f\nC_tap2 tap2 gnd 100f\nC_tap3 tap3 gnd 100f\nC_tap4 tap4 gnd 100f\n\n* =============================================\n* RESISTOR LADDER: BVDD to GND\n* =============================================\n.param rtop_l = 241\n.param r12_l  = 94\n.param r23_l  = 9.2\n.param r34_l  = 25\n.param rbot_l = 103\n\nXRtop bvdd tap1 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rtop_l\nXR12  tap1 tap2 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r12_l\nXR23  tap2 tap3 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r23_l\nXR34  tap3 tap4 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r34_l\nXRbot tap4 gnd  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rbot_l\n\n* =============================================\n* BIAS GENERATOR\n* =============================================\nXRbias bvdd nbias gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=1400\nXMnbias nbias nbias gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=99e-6\n* P-type bias\nXMpb_n pbias nbias gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=99e-6\nXMpb_p pbias pbias bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 1: tap1 vs vref — TH1 = 2.5V (POR exit)\n* =============================================\n* PMOS tail\nXM1pt c1tail pbias bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\n* PMOS diff pair: p1 gate=tap1 (mirror side), p2 gate=vref (output side)\nXM1p1 c1mi tap1 c1tail c1tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1p2 c1o  vref c1tail c1tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* NMOS mirror load\nXM1n3 c1mi c1mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM1n4 c1o  c1mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\n* Buffer: 2 inverters (non-inverting)\nXM1iv1p c1ob c1o bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1iv1n c1ob c1o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1iv2p comp1 c1ob bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1iv2n comp1 c1ob gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 2: tap2 vs vref — TH2 = 4.2V\n* =============================================\nXM2pt c2tail pbias bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM2p1 c2mi tap2 c2tail c2tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2p2 c2o  vref c2tail c2tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2n3 c2mi c2mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM2n4 c2o  c2mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM2iv1p c2ob c2o bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2iv1n c2ob c2o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2iv2p comp2 c2ob bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2iv2n comp2 c2ob gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 3: tap3 vs vref — TH3 = 4.5V\n* =============================================\nXM3pt c3tail pbias bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM3p1 c3mi tap3 c3tail c3tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3p2 c3o  vref c3tail c3tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3n3 c3mi c3mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM3n4 c3o  c3mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM3iv1p c3ob c3o bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3iv1n c3ob c3o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3iv2p comp3 c3ob bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3iv2n comp3 c3ob gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 4: tap4 vs vref — TH4 = 5.6V\n* =============================================\nXM4pt c4tail pbias bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM4p1 c4mi tap4 c4tail c4tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM4p2 c4o  vref c4tail c4tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM4n3 c4mi c4mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM4n4 c4o  c4mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM4iv1p c4ob c4o bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM4iv1n c4ob c4o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM4iv2p comp4 c4ob bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM4iv2n comp4 c4ob gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* LOGIC DECODING\n* =============================================\n* Inverted comparator outputs\nXMinv1p comp1b comp1 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv1n comp1b comp1 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv2p comp2b comp2 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv2n comp2b comp2 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv3p comp3b comp3 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv3n comp3b comp3 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv4p comp4b comp4 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv4n comp4b comp4 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* --- pass_off = NOT(comp1) = comp1b ---\nXRpo_pu bvdd pass_off gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=50\nXMpo_bufp pass_off comp1b bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMpo_bufn pass_off comp1b gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* --- bypass_en = comp1·comp2b + comp3·comp4b ---\n* AOI22: bypass_enb = NOT(bypass_en) = (comp1b+comp2)·(comp3b+comp4)\n* NMOS pull-down: series pairs in parallel\nXMby_n1a by_s1     comp1  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_n1b bypass_enb comp2b by_s1 by_s1 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_n2a by_s2     comp3  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_n2b bypass_enb comp4b by_s2 by_s2 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* PMOS pull-up: Group1=(comp1b+comp2)→gates comp1,comp2b; Group2=(comp3b+comp4)→gates comp3,comp4b\nXMby_p1a by_pmid comp1  bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p1b by_pmid comp2b bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p2a bypass_enb comp3  by_pmid by_pmid sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p2b bypass_enb comp4b by_pmid by_pmid sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\n* Output inverter\nXMby_outp bypass_en bypass_enb bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_outn bypass_en bypass_enb gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* --- ea_en = comp2·comp3b + comp4 ---\n* AOI: ea_enb = (comp2b+comp3)·comp4b\nXMea_n1a ea_s1  comp2  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMea_n1b ea_enb comp3b ea_s1 ea_s1 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20