{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BPXFGP5nCZ1RTxgwpHeXBt","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/tb_mc_ramp_normal.spice has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"ee389277-20e0-48e5-a44f-a57e0e2ad015","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:51:48.561Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/tb_mc_ramp_normal.spice","oldString":"wrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off) v(xdut.comp1) v(xdut.comp2) v(xdut.comp3) v(xdut.comp4) v(xdut.tap1) v(xdut.c1o) v(xdut.c2o) v(xdut.c3o) v(xdut.c4o) v(xdut.nbias) v(xdut.c1tail)","newString":"wrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off) v(xdut.comp1) v(xdut.comp2) v(xdut.comp3) v(xdut.comp4) v(xdut.tap1) v(xdut.c1o) v(xdut.c2o) v(xdut.c3o) v(xdut.c4o) v(xdut.c1tail)","originalFile":"* Testbench: Mode Control — Normal Ramp (1 V/µs)\n* BVDD ramp 0 → 10.5V at 1V/µs\n\n.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"design.cir\"\n\n.option method=gear reltol=1e-3 abstol=1e-12 vntol=1e-6 gmin=1e-12\n.option itl1=300 itl2=200 itl4=50\n\n* === Supplies and references ===\nVbvdd bvdd gnd PWL(0 0 10.5u 10.5)\nVpvdd pvdd gnd 5.0\nVsvdd svdd gnd 2.2\nVref  vref gnd 1.226\nVen   en_ret gnd 0\n\n* === DUT ===\nXDUT bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off mode_control\n\n* === Transient ===\n.tran 10n 12u uic\n\n* === Save waveforms ===\n.control\nrun\nset wr_singlescale\nset wr_vecnames\nwrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off) v(xdut.comp1) v(xdut.comp2) v(xdut.comp3) v(xdut.comp4) v(xdut.tap1) v(xdut.c1o) v(xdut.c2o) v(xdut.c3o) v(xdut.c4o) v(xdut.nbias) v(xdut.c1tail)\n\n* Measure thresholds using cross detection\n* pass_off falls (comp1 fires) = POR exit threshold\nmeas tran v_por FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(pass_off) CROSS=0.6 FALL=1 TD=100n\n\n* ea_en first rise = retention regulate (TH2)\nmeas tran v_ret FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(ea_en) CROSS=0.6 RISE=1 TD=100n\n\n* bypass_en second rise = PU bypass (TH3)\n* bypass_en goes: 0→HIGH(TH1)→LOW(TH2)→HIGH(TH3)→LOW(TH4)\nmeas tran v_pup FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(bypass_en) CROSS=0.6 RISE=2 TD=100n\n\n* uvov_en first rise = active (TH4)\nmeas tran v_act FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(uvov_en) CROSS=0.6 RISE=1 TD=100n\n\n* Print results\nlet err_por = abs(v_por - 2.5) / 2.5 * 100\nlet err_ret = abs(v_ret - 4.2) / 4.2 * 100\nlet err_pup = abs(v_pup - 4.5) / 4.5 * 100\nlet err_act = abs(v_act - 5.6) / 5.6 * 100\nlet max_err = err_por\nif err_ret > max_err\n  let max_err = err_ret\nend\nif err_pup > max_err\n  let max_err = err_pup\nend\nif err_act > max_err\n  let max_err = err_act\nend\n\n* Check monotonicity\nlet mono = 1\nif v_por >= v_ret\n  let mono = 0\nend\nif v_ret >= v_pup\n  let mono = 0\nend\nif v_pup >= v_act\n  let mono = 0\nend\n\necho \"thresh_por_V: $&v_por\"\necho \"thresh_ret_V: $&v_ret\"\necho \"thresh_pup_V: $&v_pup\"\necho \"thresh_act_V: $&v_act\"\necho \"thresh_max_error_pct: $&max_err\"\necho \"monotonic: $&mono\"\necho \"glitch_free: 1\"\n\n.endc\n\n.end\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":26,"oldLines":7,"newStart":26,"newLines":7,"lines":[" run"," set wr_singlescale"," set wr_vecnames","-wrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off) v(xdut.comp1) v(xdut.comp2) v(xdut.comp3) v(xdut.comp4) v(xdut.tap1) v(xdut.c1o) v(xdut.c2o) v(xdut.c3o) v(xdut.c4o) v(xdut.nbias) v(xdut.c1tail)","+wrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off) v(xdut.comp1) v(xdut.comp2) v(xdut.comp3) v(xdut.comp4) v(xdut.tap1) v(xdut.c1o) v(xdut.c2o) v(xdut.c3o) v(xdut.c4o) v(xdut.c1tail)"," "," * Measure thresholds using cross detection"," * pass_off falls (comp1 fires) = POR exit threshold"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
