{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01X1DNu4BBtJMMvL8Sd8hmkp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011H6nB49ZVcv2qAHq9zMVpK","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/design.cir","content":"* Block 08: Mode Control\n* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n*\n* NMOS diff pair + PMOS mirror + cross-coupled NMOS regeneration.\n* Swapped diff pair: vref on mirror side, tap on output side.\n*   When tap > vref: c_o drops → single inverter → comp = HIGH\n* Cross-coupled NMOS accelerates transitions via positive feedback.\n* Tail biased by vref for instant response (no RC delay).\n*\n.subckt mode_control bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off\n\n* =============================================\n* RESISTOR LADDER\n* =============================================\n.param rtop_l = 241\n.param r12_l  = 94\n.param r23_l  = 9.2\n.param r34_l  = 25\n.param rbot_l = 103\n\nXRtop bvdd tap1 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rtop_l\nXR12  tap1 tap2 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r12_l\nXR23  tap2 tap3 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r23_l\nXR34  tap3 tap4 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r34_l\nXRbot tap4 gnd  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rbot_l\n\nC_tap1 tap1 gnd 100f\nC_tap2 tap2 gnd 100f\nC_tap3 tap3 gnd 100f\nC_tap4 tap4 gnd 100f\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 1: tap1 vs vref — TH1 = 2.5V\n* =============================================\n* PMOS mirror load\nXM1p3 c1mi c1mi bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1p4 c1o  c1mi bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* NMOS diff pair: n1 gate=vref (mirror side), n2 gate=tap1 (output side)\nXM1n1 c1mi vref c1tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1n2 c1o  tap1 c1tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* Tail current (vref gate, L=50u for ~2.5µA)\nXM1t  c1tail vref gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\n* Cross-coupled NMOS positive feedback (accelerates transitions)\nXM1fb1 c1mi c1o  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM1fb2 c1o  c1mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\n* Single inverter buffer: comp1 = NOT(c1o)\n* When tap > vref: c1o drops → comp1 = HIGH ✓\nXM1ivp comp1 c1o bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1ivn comp1 c1o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 2: tap2 vs vref — TH2 = 4.2V\n* =============================================\nXM2p3 c2mi c2mi bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2p4 c2o  c2mi bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2n1 c2mi vref c2tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2n2 c2o  tap2 c2tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2t  c2tail vref gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM2fb1 c2mi c2o  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM2fb2 c2o  c2mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM2ivp comp2 c2o bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2ivn comp2 c2o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 3: tap3 vs vref — TH3 = 4.5V\n* =============================================\nXM3p3 c3mi c3mi bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3p4 c3o  c3mi bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3n1 c3mi vref c3tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3n2 c3o  tap3 c3tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3t  c3tail vref gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM3fb1 c3mi c3o  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM3fb2 c3o  c3mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM3ivp comp3 c3o bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_