{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VAg2tQ28bsSZcZUegABUeE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01XuCMB5htNkHH3sy33SGa9o","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/design.cir","content":"* Block 08: Mode Control — v5 (resistive-load comparators)\n* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n*\n* Resistive-load OTA: much faster than PMOS-mirror because R has zero Cgs\n* Lower gain but sufficient when followed by CMOS inverter buffer.\n* UNITS: MOSFETs = SI (meters), Resistors = µm\n*\n.subckt mode_control bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off\n\n* =============================================\n* RESISTOR LADDER\n* =============================================\n.param rtop_l = 241\n.param r12_l  = 94\n.param r23_l  = 9.2\n.param r34_l  = 25\n.param rbot_l = 103\n\nXRtop bvdd tap1 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rtop_l\nXR12  tap1 tap2 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r12_l\nXR23  tap2 tap3 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r23_l\nXR34  tap3 tap4 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r34_l\nXRbot tap4 gnd  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rbot_l\n\nC_tap1 tap1 gnd 100f\nC_tap2 tap2 gnd 100f\nC_tap3 tap3 gnd 100f\nC_tap4 tap4 gnd 100f\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 1: tap1 vs vref — TH1 = 2.5V\n* =============================================\n* Resistive loads (~500kΩ each, l=240µm)\nXR1ld1 bvdd c1on gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=240\nXR1ld2 bvdd c1o  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=240\n* NMOS diff pair: n1 gate=tap1 (+), n2 gate=vref (-)\n* c1o goes HIGH when tap1 > vref (more current through M1n1 → c1on drops → c1o rises)\n* Wait: with resistive loads: I_n1 > I_n2 → c1on drops (more voltage across R1ld1)\n* c1o = BVDD - I_n2 * R → c1o rises (less voltage drop)\n* So c1o goes HIGH when tap > vref ✓\nXM1n1 c1on tap1 c1tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1n2 c1o  vref c1tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* Tail: vref-biased NMOS\nXM1t  c1tail vref gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\n* Buffer: 2 inverters (non-inverting: comp1 = c1o HIGH → comp1 HIGH)\nXM1iv1p c1ob c1o bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1iv1n c1ob c1o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1iv2p comp1 c1ob bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1iv2n comp1 c1ob gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 2: tap2 vs vref — TH2 = 4.2V\n* =============================================\nXR2ld1 bvdd c2on gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=240\nXR2ld2 bvdd c2o  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=240\nXM2n1 c2on tap2 c2tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2n2 c2o  vref c2tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2t  c2tail vref gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM2iv1p c2ob c2o bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2iv1n c2ob c2o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2iv2p comp2 c2ob bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2iv2n comp2 c2ob gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 3: tap3 vs vref — TH3 = 4.5V\n* =============================================\nXR3ld1 bvdd c3on gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=240\nXR3ld2 bvdd c3o  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=240\nXM3n1 c3on tap3 c3tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3n2 c3o  vref c3tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3t  c3tail vref gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=50e-6\nXM3iv1p c3ob c3o bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3iv1n c3ob c3o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3iv2p comp3 c3ob bvdd bvdd sk