{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01GmhxaAgkp9M9NTyh3Q6Kkg","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Mi88KMFVRkCjzqZ1bGuXTM","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/design.cir","content":"* Block 08: Mode Control — v6 (PVDD-powered comparators)\n* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n*\n* Comparators powered from PVDD (fixed 5V) for constant speed/headroom.\n* During POR (PVDD=0), comp outputs default LOW → correct behavior.\n* Logic powered from BVDD for correct output levels.\n*\n.subckt mode_control bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off\n\n* =============================================\n* RESISTOR LADDER\n* =============================================\n.param rtop_l = 241\n.param r12_l  = 94\n.param r23_l  = 9.2\n.param r34_l  = 25\n.param rbot_l = 103\n\nXRtop bvdd tap1 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rtop_l\nXR12  tap1 tap2 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r12_l\nXR23  tap2 tap3 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r23_l\nXR34  tap3 tap4 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r34_l\nXRbot tap4 gnd  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rbot_l\nC_tap1 tap1 gnd 100f\nC_tap2 tap2 gnd 100f\nC_tap3 tap3 gnd 100f\nC_tap4 tap4 gnd 100f\n\n* =============================================\n* BIAS from PVDD: resistor + diode NMOS → ~2µA constant\n* =============================================\nXRbias pvdd nbias gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=900\nXMnbias nbias nbias gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 1: tap1 vs vref — TH1 = 2.5V\n* =============================================\n* PMOS mirror load from PVDD\nXM1p3 c1on c1on pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1p4 c1o  c1on pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* NMOS diff pair\nXM1n1 c1on tap1 c1tail gnd sky130_fd_