{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_012DV7vhFRgBooGUXaaaZYAL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011EvEQvrbXUPcgEHAhqLJJW","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/design.cir","content":"* Block 08: Mode Control — v7 (PVDD-powered, high-current, fast)\n* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n*\n* Comparators from PVDD (constant 5V). High tail current (24µA) for fast slew.\n* Iq spec is from BVDD → comparator PVDD current doesn't count.\n* Swapped diff pair: c_o drops when tap>vref. Single inverter: comp=HIGH when tap>vref.\n*\n.subckt mode_control bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off\n\n* =============================================\n* RESISTOR LADDER (from BVDD)\n* =============================================\n.param rtop_l = 241\n.param r12_l  = 94\n.param r23_l  = 9.2\n.param r34_l  = 25\n.param rbot_l = 103\n\nXRtop bvdd tap1 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rtop_l\nXR12  tap1 tap2 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r12_l\nXR23  tap2 tap3 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r23_l\nXR34  tap3 tap4 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=r34_l\nXRbot tap4 gnd  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=rbot_l\nC_tap1 tap1 gnd 100f\nC_tap2 tap2 gnd 100f\nC_tap3 tap3 gnd 100f\nC_tap4 tap4 gnd 100f\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 1: tap1 vs vref — TH1 = 2.5V\n* =============================================\n* PMOS mirror from PVDD\nXM1p3 c1mi c1mi pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1p4 c1o  c1mi pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* Swapped diff pair: vref on mirror side, tap on output side\nXM1n1 c1mi vref c1tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1n2 c1o  tap1 c1tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* High-current tail: W=80µm for ~24µA\nXM1t  c1tail vref gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=80e-6 l=20e-6\n* Single inverter: comp1 = NOT(c1o) = HIGH when tap>vref\nXM1ivp comp1 c1o pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1ivn comp1 c1o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 2: tap2 vs vref — TH2 = 4.2V\n* =============================================\nXM2p3 c2mi c2mi pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2p4 c2o  c2mi pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2n1 c2mi vref c2tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2n2 c2o  tap2 c2tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2t  c2tail vref gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=80e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2ivp comp2 c2o pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2ivn comp2 c2o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 3: tap3 vs vref — TH3 = 4.5V\n* =============================================\nXM3p3 c3mi c3mi pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3p4 c3o  c3mi pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3n1 c3mi vref c3tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3n2 c3o  tap3 c3tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3t  c3tail vref gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=80e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3ivp comp3 c3o pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3ivn comp3 c3o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 4: tap4 vs vref — TH4 = 5.6V\n* =============================================\nXM4p3 c4mi c4mi pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM4p4 c4o  c4mi pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM4n1 c4mi vref c4tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM4n2 c4o  tap4 c4tail gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM4t  c4tail vref gnd gnd sky130_fd