s vref — TH1 = 2.5V\n* =============================================\n* PMOS tail\nXM1pt c1tail pbias pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* PMOS diff pair: p1 gate=tap (mirror side), p2 gate=vref (output side)\nXM1p1 c1mi tap1 c1tail c1tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1p2 c1o  vref c1tail c1tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* NMOS mirror load\nXM1n3 c1mi c1mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1n4 c1o  c1mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* 2-inverter buffer (from PVDD): comp1 = c1o polarity\nXM1iv1p c1ob c1o pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1iv1n c1ob c1o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1iv2p comp1 c1ob pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM1iv2n comp1 c1ob gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 2: tap2 vs vref — TH2 = 4.2V\n* =============================================\nXM2pt c2tail pbias pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2p1 c2mi tap2 c2tail c2tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2p2 c2o  vref c2tail c2tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2n3 c2mi c2mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2n4 c2o  c2mi gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2iv1p c2ob c2o pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2iv1n c2ob c2o gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2iv2p comp2 c2ob pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXM2iv2n comp2 c2ob gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATOR 3: tap3 vs vref — TH3 = 4.5V\n* =============================================\nXM3pt c3tail pbias pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3p1 c3mi tap3 c3tail c3tail sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXM3p2 