pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","+* PMOS diff pair (body=pvdd)","+XMp1 mi  tap_in ctail pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","+XMp2 out vref   ctail pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","+"," * NMOS mirror","-XMn3 mirror_in mirror_in 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","-XMn4 ota_out   mirror_in 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","+XMn3 mi  mi 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","+XMn4 out mi 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6"," ","-.dc Vtap 0 2.5 0.25","+.dc Vtap 0 2.5 0.1"," "," .control"," run","-echo \"vtap     ota_out    mirror_in  ctail\"","-print v(vtap_node) v(ota_out) v(mirror_in) v(ctail)","+echo \"vtap     out        mi         ctail\"","+print v(tap_in) v(out) v(mi) v(ctail)"," .endc"," "," .end"]}],"originalFile":"* Minimal test: does the OTA output follow tap?\n.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n\nVpvdd pvdd 0 5.0\nVref  vref 0 1.226\nVtap  vtap_node  0 dc\n\n* Bias\nXMpb pbias pbias pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nRpb pbias 0 180000\n\n* Tail\nXMpt ctail pbias pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* Diff pair\nXMp1 mirror_in vtap_node ctail pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMp2 ota_out   vref      ctail pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n* NMOS mirror\nXMn3 mirror_in mirror_in 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMn4 ota_out   mirror_in 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n.dc Vtap 0 2.5 0.25\n\n.control\nrun\necho \"vtap     ota_out    mirror_in  ctail\"\nprint v(vtap_node) v(ota_out) v(mirror_in) v(ctail)\n.endc\n\n.end\n"}}
