{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013vwaUyonuL9Bo8ipAqebfF","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/tb_mc_ramp_normal.spice has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"ccad40a2-fc15-45a3-9cd4-e7dfd87984ba","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:35:49.061Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/tb_mc_ramp_normal.spice","oldString":"wrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off) v(xdut.comp1) v(xdut.comp2) v(xdut.comp3) v(xdut.comp4)","newString":"wrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off) v(xdut.comp1) v(xdut.comp2) v(xdut.comp3) v(xdut.comp4) v(xdut.c1tap) v(xdut.c1inv)","originalFile":"* Testbench: Mode Control — Normal Ramp (1 V/µs)\n.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"design.cir\"\n\n.option method=gear reltol=1e-3 abstol=1e-12 vntol=1e-6 gmin=1e-12\n.option itl1=300 itl2=200 itl4=50\n\nVbvdd bvdd gnd PWL(0 0 10.5u 10.5)\nVpvdd pvdd gnd 5.0\nVsvdd svdd gnd 2.2\nVref  vref gnd 1.226\nVen   en_ret gnd 0\n\nXDUT bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off mode_control\n\n.tran 10n 12u uic\n\n.control\nrun\nset wr_singlescale\nset wr_vecnames\nwrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off) v(xdut.comp1) v(xdut.comp2) v(xdut.comp3) v(xdut.comp4)\n\n* Measure comp transitions: find where comp crosses 50% of BVDD\n* Use fixed thresholds at different levels to detect rising edges\nmeas tran v_c1_r FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp1) CROSS=1.5 RISE=1 TD=500n\nmeas tran v_c2_r FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp2) CROSS=1.5 RISE=1 TD=500n\nmeas tran v_c3_r FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp3) CROSS=1.5 RISE=1 TD=500n\nmeas tran v_c4_r FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp4) CROSS=1.5 RISE=1 TD=500n\n\necho \"=== Comparator Firing Points ===\"\necho \"comp1_fires_at: $&v_c1_r\"\necho \"comp2_fires_at: $&v_c2_r\"\necho \"comp3_fires_at: $&v_c3_r\"\necho \"comp4_fires_at: $&v_c4_r\"\n\n* Check output transitions\nmeas tran v_po_f FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(pass_off) CROSS=1.0 FALL=1 TD=500n\nmeas tran v_by_r FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(bypass_en) CROSS=1.0 RISE=1 TD=500n\nmeas tran v_ea_r FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(ea_en) CROSS=1.0 RISE=1 TD=500n\nmeas tran v_uv_r FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(uvov_en) CROSS=1.0 RISE=1 TD=500n\necho \"pass_off_falls: $&v_po_f\"\necho \"bypass_en_rises: $&v_by_r\"\necho \"ea_en_rises: $&v_ea_r\"\necho \"uvov_en_rises: $&v_uv_r\"\n\n* Calculate threshold errors if measurements succeeded\nif v_c1_r > 0\n  let err1 = abs(v_c1_r - 2.5)/2.5*100\n  let err2 = abs(v_c2_r - 4.2)/4.2*100\n  let err3 = abs(v_c3_r - 4.5)/4.5*100\n  let err4 = abs(v_c4_r - 5.6)/5.6*100\n  echo \"thresh_por_V: $&v_c1_r\"\n  echo \"thresh_ret_V: $&v_c2_r\"\n  echo \"thresh_pup_V: $&v_c3_r\"\n  echo \"thresh_act_V: $&v_c4_r\"\nend\n\n.endc\n\n.end\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":20,"oldLines":7,"newStart":20,"newLines":7,"lines":[" run"," set wr_singlescale"," set wr_vecnames","-wrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off) v(xdut.comp1) v(xdut.comp2) v(xdut.comp3) v(xdut.comp4)","+wrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off) v(xdut.comp1) v(xdut.comp2) v(xdut.comp3) v(xdut.comp4) v(xdut.c1tap) v(xdut.c1inv)"," "," * Measure comp transitions: find where comp crosses 50% of BVDD"," * Use fixed thresholds at different levels to detect rising edges"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
