{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Bs3FMqMTetDQmbwX3QsLSD","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**comp1 now transitions at BVDD ≈ 3.22-3.35V!** The c1inv (first inverter output) crosses midpoint at c1tap ≈ 2.0-2.1V when BVDD ≈ 3.0-3.1V.\n\nThis is much better (3.3V vs 4.0V before), but still 0.8V above the 2.5V target. The divider ratio needs further adjustment. The c1tap = 1.82V at the theoretical trip should occur at BVDD = 1.82/0.73 = 2.49V. But due to RC lag, c1tap only reaches 1.82V at BVDD ≈ 2.82V (0.33V lag).\n\nLet me commit this progress and continue tuning."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1388,"cache_read_input_tokens":394165,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1388},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"a869113c-3dab-4a9c-99a2-538fdb04828a"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Bs3FMqMTetDQmbwX3QsLSD","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013gwonm4UJEVL1sWHN19sYN","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips && git add pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/ && git commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nexp(08): PMOS diff pair comps from PVDD + inverter-based comp1\n\nFixed body connections (body=source for diff pair), bias resistor\ndirection (pulldown not pullup). Comp1 uses CMOS inverter threshold\ndetector with separate voltage divider from BVDD. Comp2-4 use PMOS\ndiff pair OTAs from PVDD.\n\nCurrent status: comp1 fires at BVDD~3.3V (target 2.5V), comp2 at ~3.9V\n(target 4.2V). Need to tune divider ratio and reduce RC lag for comp1.\nOTA comparators still have slew rate limitations with HV devices.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\"","description":"Commit progress"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1388,"cache_read_input_tokens":394165,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1388},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"f87de164-666e-40ca-afb5-ce254d7df9c7"}
