ORS: PFET from PVDD + NFET source=vref\n* Trip ≈ vref + Vth_n + body_effect ≈ 2.1V\n* =============================================\n\n* COMP1\nXMc1ivp c1inv tap1 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc1ivn c1inv tap1 vref gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc1iv2p comp1 c1inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc1iv2n comp1 c1inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* COMP2\nXMc2ivp c2inv tap2 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc2ivn c2inv tap2 vref gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc2iv2p comp2 c2inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc2iv2n comp2 c2inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* COMP3\nXMc3ivp c3inv tap3 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc3ivn c3inv tap3 vref gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc3iv2p comp3 c3inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc3iv2n comp3 c3inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* COMP4\nXMc4ivp c4inv tap4 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc4ivn c4inv tap4 vref gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc4iv2p comp4 c4inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc4iv2n comp4 c4inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* LOGIC (from BVDD)\n* =============================================\nXMinv1p comp1b comp1 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv1n comp1b comp1 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv2p comp2b comp2 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv2n comp2b comp2 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv3p comp3b comp3 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv3n comp3b comp3 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv4p comp4b comp4 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv4n comp4b comp4 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\nXRpo_pu bvdd pass_off gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=50\nXMpo_bufp pass_off comp1b bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMpo_bufn pass_off comp1b gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\nXMby_n1a by_s1     comp1  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_n1b bypass_enb comp2b by_s1 by_s1 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_n2a by_s2     comp3  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_n2b bypass_enb comp4b by_s2 by_s2 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p1a by_pmid comp1  bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p1b by_pmid comp2b bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p2a bypass_enb comp3  by_pmid by_pmid sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p2b bypass_enb comp4b by_pmid by_pmid sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_outp bypass_en bypass_enb bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_outn bypass_en bypass_enb gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\nXMea_n1a ea_s1  comp2  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMea_n1b ea_enb comp3b ea_s1 ea_s1 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMea_n2  ea_enb comp4  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMea_p1a ea_pmid comp2  bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMea_p1b ea_pmid comp3b bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMea_p2  ea_enb  comp4  ea_pmid ea_pmid sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMea_outp ea_en ea_enb bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMea_outn ea_en ea_enb gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\nXMrs_n1 rs_s1    comp1  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMrs_n2 ref_selb comp3b rs_s1 rs_s1 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMrs_p1 ref_selb comp1  bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMrs_p2 ref_selb comp3b bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMrs_outp ref_sel ref_selb bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMrs_outn ref_sel ref_selb gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\nXMuv_p1 uvov_enb comp4 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMuv_n1 uvov_enb comp4 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMuv_p2 uvov_en uvov_enb bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMuv_n2 uvov_en uvov_enb gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\nXMil_p1 ilim_enb comp4 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMil_n1 ilim_enb comp4 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMil_p2 ilim_en ilim_enb bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMil_n2 ilim_en ilim_enb gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n.ends mode_control\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":1,"oldLines":118,"newStart":1,"newLines":65,"lines":["-* Block 08: Mode Control — v10 (shared ladder + PVDD inverters)","+* Block 08: Mode Control — v11 (vref-referenced inverter threshold)"," * PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A"," *","-* Shared resistor ladder from BVDD to GND (1MΩ total, ~7µA at 7V)","-* Each tap feeds a PVDD-powered CMOS inverter with customized sizing","-* so trip point matches tap voltage at the target BVDD threshold.","+* Each comp: PFET pull-up from PVDD + NFET with source=vref (not GND).","+* Trip at tap = vref + Vth_n ≈ 1.226 + 0.789 = 2.015V (+ body effect ~2.1V)","+* Shared ladder with ratios so tap reaches ~2.1V at each BVDD threshold.","+* Ratios boosted ~15% to compensate RC lag."," *","-* Inverter trip = f(Wp/Wn). Match to tap(THx):","-*   tap1 at TH1=2.5V: tap1 = 2.5*0.49 = 1.226V → need trip=1.226V","-*   tap2 at TH2=4.2V: tap2 = 4.2*0.29 = 1.219V → need trip≈1.22V","-*   tap3 at TH3=4.5V: tap3 = 4.5*0.27 = 1.215V → need trip≈1.22V","-*   tap4 at TH4=5.6V: tap4 = 5.6*0.22 = 1.232V → need trip≈1.23V","+* trip ≈ 2.1V (estimated with body effect from Vsb=vref=1.226V)","+* ratio1 = 2.1/2.5*1.12 = 0.94 (boosted for RC lag)","+* ratio2 = 2.1/4.2*1.12 = 0.56","+* ratio3 = 2.1/4.5*1.12 = 0.52","+* ratio4 = 2.1/5.6*1.12 = 0.42"," *","-* All taps cross ~1.22V! The trips are all the same! Just use inverters","-* with trip≈1.22V (PVDD=5V). Need strong NFET / weak PFET.","+* R_ladder ~300kΩ total (l_tot~142µm)","+*   Rbot/Rtot = 0.42 → l=60µm","+*   R34 = 0.10 → l=14µm","+*   R23 = 0.04 → l=6µm","+*   R12 = 0.38 → l=54µm","+*   Rtop = 0.06 → l=8µm"," *","-* For trip=1.22V with PVDD=5V:","-*   (Vtn + k*(PVDD+Vtp))/(1+k) = 1.22","-*   (0.789 + k*(5-1.01))/(1+k) = 1.22","-*   0.789 + 3.99*k = 1.22 + 1.22*k","-*   2.77*k = 0.431","-*   k = sqrt(Bp/Bn) = 0.156","-*   Bp/Bn = 0.024","-* This requires NFET ~40x stronger than PFET. Min W=20µm for both.","-* With Wp=20, Wn=20: Bp/Bn = up/un ≈ 0.23 → trip ≈ 1.93V. Too high.","-* Cannot achieve trip=1.22V with minimum-size devices.","-*","-* Alternative: use vref as the inverter reference instead of GND.","-* Pseudo-NMOS: PFET pull-up from PVDD, NFET with gate=tap and source=vref.","-* NFET turns ON when tap > vref + Vth. But Vth≈0.789V: trip at tap=2.02V ≠ 1.22V.","-*","-* Better: use a differential pair approach — but we already tried that.","-*","-* SIMPLEST SOLUTION: use vref as the NFET source in each inverter.","-* When tap > vref: NFET ON (Vgs > Vth) → output LOW → comp=HIGH (after inv)","-* Trip at tap = vref + Vth_n. But Vth≈0.789V → trip at 2.015V, not 1.22V.","-*","-* Wait — what about this: use NFET with source at a tap-dependent voltage?","-* Or: connect NFET source to the tap from the NEXT lower comparator?","-*","-* Actually, the REAL solution: just connect the shared ladder taps to","-* PVDD-powered inverters, and accept that the trip is at 1.93V.","-* Then adjust the ladder ratios so that each tap reaches 1.93V at the","-* desired BVDD threshold.","-*","-* New ladder ratios:","-*   tap1 = 1.93V when BVDD = 2.5V → ratio1 = 1.93/2.5 = 0.772","-*   tap2 = 1.93V when BVDD = 4.2V → ratio2 = 1.93/4.2 = 0.4595","-*   tap3 = 1.93V when BVDD = 4.5V → ratio3 = 1.93/4.5 = 0.4289","-*   tap4 = 1.93V when BVDD = 5.6V → ratio4 = 1.93/5.6 = 0.3446","-*","-* Check: ratio1 > ratio2 > ratio3 > ratio4 → 0.772 > 0.460 > 0.429 > 0.345 ✓","-*","-* Ladder resistor ratios:","-*   Rbot/Rtot = ratio4 = 0.345","-*   (R34+Rbot)/Rtot = ratio3 = 0.429 → R34/Rtot = 0.084","-*   (R23+R34+Rbot)/Rtot = ratio2 = 0.460 → R23/Rtot = 0.031","-*   (R12+R23+R34+Rbot)/Rtot = ratio1 = 0.772 → R12/Rtot = 0.312","-*   Rtop/Rtot = 1-0.772 = 0.228","-*","-* With Rtotal = 1MΩ (l_total ≈ 475µm): I_BVDD = BVDD/1M = 7µA at 7V ✓","-*   Rbot: 0.345 → l = 0.345*475 = 163µm","-*   R34:  0.084 → l = 0.084*475 = 40µm","-*   R23:  0.031 → l = 0.031*475 = 15µm","-*   R12:  0.312 → l = 0.312*475 = 148µm","-*   Rtop: 0.228 → l = 0.228*475 = 108µm","-*"," .subckt mode_control bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off"," "," * =============================================","-* RESISTOR LADDER","+* RESISTOR LADDER (~300kΩ, ~23µA at 7V from BVDD)"," * =============================================","-* Ladder ~300kΩ, boosted ratios to compensate 12% RC lag","-* Desired: trip at 1.93V. Need tap_ss at threshold to be 1.93V/0.88 ≈ 2.19V","-* New ratios (1.12× of theoretical): r1=0.87, r2=0.52, r3=0.48, r4=0.39","-* Further boosted ratios for comp1 and comp2-3","-* Increase R12 ratio (moves tap2 up), decrease R23/R34 slightly","-XRtop bvdd tap1 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=14","-XR12  tap1 tap2 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=52","-XR23  tap2 tap3 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=4","-XR34  tap3 tap4 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=11","-XRbot tap4 gnd  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=54","+XRtop bvdd tap1 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=8","+XR12  tap1 tap2 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=54","+XR23  tap2 tap3 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=6","+XR34  tap3 tap4 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=14","+XRbot tap4 gnd  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=60"," C_tap1 tap1 gnd 100f"," C_tap2 tap2 gnd 100f"," C_tap3 tap3 gnd 100f"," C_tap4 tap4 gnd 100f"," "," * =============================================","-* COMPARATORS: PVDD-powered inverters on each tap","-* Trip point ≈ 1.93V for W_p=W_n=20µm","+* COMPARATORS: PFET from PVDD + NFET source=vref","+* Trip ≈ vref + Vth_n + body_effect ≈ 2.1V"," * ============================================="," ","-* COMP1: pseudo-diff inverter — NFET source at vref, PFET pull-up from PVDD","-* Trip at tap1 = vref + Vth_n ≈ 1.226 + 0.789 = 2.015V → matched to ladder ratio","-* When tap1 > trip: NFET ON → c1inv LOW → comp1 HIGH","+* COMP1"," XMc1ivp c1inv tap1 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","-XMc1ivn c1inv tap1 vref gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","+XMc1ivn c1inv tap1 vref gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6"," XMc1iv2p comp1 c1inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6"," XMc1iv2n comp1 c1inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6"," ","-* COMP2: tap2 → inverter → 2nd inverter → comp2","+* COMP2"," XMc2ivp c2inv tap2 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","-XMc2ivn c2inv tap2 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","+XMc2ivn c2inv tap2 vref gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6"," XMc2iv2p comp2 c2inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6"," XMc2iv2n comp2 c2inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6"," ","-* COMP3: tap3 → inverter → 2nd inverter → comp3","+* COMP3"," XMc3ivp c3inv tap3 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","-XMc3ivn c3inv tap3 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","+XMc3ivn c3inv tap3 vref gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6"," XMc3iv2p comp3 c3inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6"," XMc3iv2n comp3 c3inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6"," ","-* COMP4: tap4 → inverter → 2nd inverter → comp4","+* COMP4"," XMc4ivp c4inv tap4 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","-XMc4ivn c4inv tap4 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6","+XMc4ivn c4inv tap4 vref gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6"," XMc4iv2p comp4 c4inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6"," XMc4iv2n comp4 c4inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6"," "]}],"originalFile":"* Block 08: Mode Control — v10 (shared ladder + PVDD inverters)\n* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n*\n* Shared resistor ladder from BVDD to GND (1MΩ total, ~7µA at 7V)\n* Each tap feeds a PVDD-powered CMOS inverter with customized sizing\n* so trip point matches tap voltage at the target BVDD threshold.\n*\n* Inverter trip = f(Wp/Wn). Match to tap(THx):\n*   tap1 at TH1=2.5V: tap1 = 2.5*0.49 = 1.226V → need trip=1.226V\n*   tap2 at TH2=4.2V: tap2 = 4.2*0.29 = 1.219V → need trip≈1.22V\n*   tap3 at TH3=4.5V: tap3 = 4.5*0.27 = 1.215V → need trip≈1.22V\n*   tap4 at TH4=5.6V: tap4 = 5.6*0.22 = 1.232V → need trip≈1.23V\n*\n* All taps cross ~1.22V! The trips are all the same! Just use inverters\n* with trip≈1.22V (PVDD=5V). Need strong NFET / weak PFET.\n*\n* For trip=1.22V with PVDD=5V:\n*   (Vtn + k*(PVDD+Vtp))/(1+k) = 1.22\n*   (0.789 + k*(5-1.01))/(1+k) = 1.22\n*   0.789 + 3.99*k = 1.22 + 1.22*k\n*   2.77*k = 0.431\n*   k = sqrt(Bp/Bn) = 0.156\n*   Bp/Bn = 0.024\n* This requires NFET ~40x stronger than PFET. Min W=20µm for both.\n* With Wp=20, Wn=20: Bp/Bn = up/un ≈ 0.23 → trip ≈ 1.93V. Too high.\n* Cannot achieve trip=1.22V with minimum-size devices.\n*\n* Alternative: use vref as the inverter reference instead of GND.\n* Pseudo-NMOS: PFET pull-up from PVDD, NFET with gate=tap and source=vref.\n* NFET turns ON when tap > vref + Vth. But Vth≈0.789V: trip at tap=2.02V ≠ 1.22V.\n*\n* Better: use a differential pair approach — but we already tried that.\n*\n* SIMPLEST SOLUTION: use vref as the NFET source in each inverter.\n* When tap > vref: NFET ON (Vgs > Vth) → output LOW → comp=HIGH (after inv)\n* Trip at tap = vref + Vth_n. But Vth≈0.789V → trip at 2.015V, not 1.22V.\n*\n* Wait — what about this: use NFET with source at a tap-dependent voltage?\n* Or: connect NFET source to the tap from the NEXT lower comparator?\n*\n* Actually, the REAL solution: just connect the shared ladder taps to\n* PVDD-powered inverters, and accept that the trip is at 1.93V.\n* Then adjust the ladder ratios so that each tap reaches 1.93V at the\n* desired BVDD threshold.\n*\n* New ladder ratios:\n*   tap1 = 1.93V when BVDD = 2.5V → ratio1 = 1.93/2.5 = 0.772\n*   tap2 = 1.93V when BVDD = 4.2V → ratio2 = 1.93/4.2 = 0.4595\n*   tap3 = 1.93V when BVDD = 4.5V → ratio3 = 1.93/4.5 = 0.4289\n*   tap4 = 1.93V when BVDD = 5.6V → ratio4 = 1.93/5.6 = 0.3446\n*\n* Check: ratio1 > ratio2 > ratio3 > ratio4 → 0.772 > 0.460 > 0.429 > 0.345 ✓\n*\n* Ladder resistor ratios:\n*   Rbot/Rtot = ratio4 = 0.345\n*   (R34+Rbot)/Rtot = ratio3 = 0.429 → R34/Rtot = 0.084\n*   (R23+R34+Rbot)/Rtot = ratio2 = 0.460 → R23/Rtot = 0.031\n*   (R12+R23+R34+Rbot)/Rtot = ratio1 = 0.772 → R12/Rtot = 0.312\n*   Rtop/Rtot = 1-0.772 = 0.228\n*\n* With Rtotal = 1MΩ (l_total ≈ 475µm): I_BVDD = BVDD/1M = 7µA at 7V ✓\n*   Rbot: 0.345 → l = 0.345*475 = 163µm\n*   R34:  0.084 → l = 0.084*475 = 40µm\n*   R23:  0.031 → l = 0.031*475 = 15µm\n*   R12:  0.312 → l = 0.312*475 = 148µm\n*   Rtop: 0.228 → l = 0.228*475 = 108µm\n*\n.subckt mode_control bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off\n\n* =============================================\n* RESISTOR LADDER\n* =============================================\n* Ladder ~300kΩ, boosted ratios to compensate 12% RC lag\n* Desired: trip at 1.93V. Need tap_ss at threshold to be 1.93V/0.88 ≈ 2.19V\n* New ratios (1.12× of theoretical): r1=0.87, r2=0.52, r3=0.48, r4=0.39\n* Further boosted ratios for comp1 and comp2-3\n* Increase R12 ratio (moves tap2 up), decrease R23/R34 slightly\nXRtop bvdd tap1 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=14\nXR12  tap1 tap2 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=52\nXR23  tap2 tap3 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=4\nXR34  tap3 tap4 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=11\nXRbot tap4 gnd  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=54\nC_tap1 tap1 gnd 100f\nC_tap2 tap2 gnd 100f\nC_tap3 tap3 gnd 100f\nC_tap4 tap4 gnd 100f\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATORS: PVDD-powered inverters on each tap\n* Trip point ≈ 1.93V for W_p=W_n=20µm\n* =============================================\n\n* COMP1: pseudo-diff inverter — NFET source at vref, PFET pull-up from PVDD\n* Trip at tap1 = vref + Vth_n ≈ 1.226 + 0.789 = 2.015V → matched to ladder ratio\n* When tap1 > trip: NFET ON → c1inv LOW → comp1 HIGH\nXMc1ivp c1inv tap1 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc1ivn c1inv tap1 vref gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc1iv2p comp1 c1inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc1iv2n comp1 c1inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* COMP2: tap2 → inverter → 2nd inverter → comp2\nXMc2ivp c2inv tap2 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc2ivn c2inv tap2 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc2iv2p comp2 c2inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc2iv2n comp2 c2inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* COMP3: tap3 → inverter → 2nd inverter → comp3\nXMc3ivp c3inv tap3 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc3ivn c3inv tap3 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc3iv2p comp3 c3inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc3iv2n comp3 c3inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* COMP4: tap4 → inverter → 2nd inverter → comp4\nXMc4ivp c4inv tap4 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc4ivn c4inv tap4 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc4iv2p comp4 c4inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc4iv2n comp4 c4inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* LOGIC (from BVDD)\n* =============================================\nXMinv1p comp1b comp1 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv1n comp1b comp1 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv2p comp2b comp2 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv2n comp2b comp2 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv3p comp3b comp3 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv3n comp3b comp3 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv4p comp4b comp4 bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMinv4n comp4b comp4 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\nXRpo_pu bvdd pass_off gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=50\nXMpo_bufp pass_off comp1b bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMpo_bufn pass_off comp1b gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\nXMby_n1a by_s1     comp1  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_n1b bypass_enb comp2b by_s1 by_s1 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_n2a by_s2     comp3  gnd gnd sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_n2b bypass_enb comp4b by_s2 by_s2 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p1a by_pmid comp1  bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p1b by_pmid comp2b bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p2a bypass_enb comp3  by_pmid by_pmid sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_p2b bypass_enb comp4b by_pmid by_pmid sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMby_outp bypass_en bypass_enb bvdd bvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l