{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TavFkpfNb2B9TaH87Eyc7d","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* Block 08: Mode Control — v11 (vref-referenced inverter threshold)\n     2→* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n     3→*\n     4→* Each comp: PFET pull-up from PVDD + NFET with source=vref (not GND).\n     5→* Trip at tap = vref + Vth_n ≈ 1.226 + 0.789 = 2.015V (+ body effect ~2.1V)\n     6→* Shared ladder with ratios so tap reaches ~2.1V at each BVDD threshold.\n     7→* Ratios boosted ~15% to compensate RC lag.\n     8→*\n     9→* trip ≈ 2.1V (estimated with body effect from Vsb=vref=1.226V)\n    10→* ratio1 = 2.1/2.5*1.12 = 0.94 (boosted for RC lag)\n    11→* ratio2 = 2.1/4.2*1.12 = 0.56\n    12→* ratio3 = 2.1/4.5*1.12 = 0.52\n    13→* ratio4 = 2.1/5.6*1.12 = 0.42\n    14→*\n    15→* R_ladder ~300kΩ total (l_tot~142µm)\n    16→*   Rbot/Rtot = 0.42 → l=60µm\n    17→*   R34 = 0.10 → l=14µm\n    18→*   R23 = 0.04 → l=6µm\n    19→*   R12 = 0.38 → l=54µm\n    20→*   Rtop = 0.06 → l=8µm\n    21→*\n    22→.subckt mode_control bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off\n    23→\n    24→* =============================================\n    25→* RESISTOR LADDER (~300kΩ, ~23µA at 7V from BVDD)\n    26→* =============================================\n    27→* Ladder ~350kΩ (Iq ~20µA at 7V). Ratios boosted ~30% for RC lag compensation.\n    28→* target ratios: r1=0.96, r2=0.60, r3=0.56, r4=0.45\n    29→* Rbot=0.45*166=75, R34=0.11*166=18, R23=0.04*166=7, R12=0.36*166=60, Rtop=0.04*166=7\n    30→* Ladder ~400kΩ (Iq ~17.5µA at 7V). Scale all by 1.14x"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012y2fFofaYqh7GoHST4TjxC","session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"6f874f89-7362-490e-868f-e297d6892bf2","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:55:22.451Z"}
