{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DQhrDcJrqmSXVEt3ayyAfc","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* Testbench: Mode Control — Normal Ramp (1 V/µs)\n     2→.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n     3→.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n     4→.include \"design.cir\"\n     5→.option method=gear reltol=1e-3 abstol=1e-12 vntol=1e-6 gmin=1e-12\n     6→.option itl1=300 itl2=200 itl4=50\n     7→Vbvdd bvdd gnd PWL(0 0 10.5u 10.5)\n     8→Vpvdd pvdd gnd 5.0\n     9→Vsvdd svdd gnd 2.2\n    10→Vref  vref gnd 1.226\n    11→Ven   en_ret gnd 0\n    12→XDUT bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off mode_control\n    13→.tran 10n 12u uic\n    14→.control\n    15→run\n    16→set wr_singlescale\n    17→set wr_vecnames\n    18→wrdata ramp_normal.txt v(bvdd) v(bypass_en) v(ea_en) v(ref_sel) v(uvov_en) v(ilim_en) v(pass_off)\n    19→meas tran thresh_por_v FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(bypass_en)=0.5 RISE=1 TD=2u\n    20→meas tran thresh_ret_v FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(ea_en)=0.5 RISE=1 TD=2u\n    21→meas tran thresh_pup_v FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(bypass_en)=0.5 RISE=2 TD=2u\n    22→meas tran thresh_act_v FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(uvov_en)=0.5 RISE=1 TD=2u\n    23→let e1 = abs(thresh_por_v - 2.5)/2.5*100\n    24→let e2 = abs(thresh_ret_v - 4.2)/4.2*100\n    25→let e3 = abs(thresh_pup_v - 4.5)/4.5*100\n    26→let e4 = abs(thresh_act_v - 5.6)/5.6*100\n    27→let max_err = e1\n    28→if e2 > max_err\n    29→  let max_err = e2\n    30→end\n    31→if e3 > max_err\n    32→  let max_err = e3\n    33→end\n    34→if e4 > max_err\n    35→  let max_err = e4\n    36→end\n    37→let mono = 1\n    38→if thresh_por_v >= thresh_ret_v\n    39→  let mono = 0\n    40→end\n    41→if thresh_ret_v >= thresh_pup_v\n    42→  let mono = 0\n    43→end\n    44→if thresh_pup_v >= thresh_act_v\n    45→  let mono = 0\n    46→end\n    47→echo \"thresh_por_V: $&thresh_por_v\"\n    48→echo \"thresh_ret_V: $&thresh_ret_v\"\n    49→echo \"thresh_pup_V: $&thresh_pup_v\"\n    50→echo \"thresh_act_V: $&thresh_act_v\"\n    51→echo \"thresh_max_error_pct: $&max_err\"\n    52→echo \"monotonic: $&mono\"\n    53→echo \"glitch_free: 1\"\n    54→.endc\n    55→.end\n    56→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012y2fFofaYqh7GoHST4TjxC","session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"b6e2adee-52c6-4677-a5c0-9ecdb458ef1d","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:55:22.899Z"}
