{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Dtx1KBrUzNPSkwhHKAecWM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_017B3Kr2oeCGbkS4HeEHKbji","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/tb_mc_slow_ramp.spice"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3065,"cache_read_input_tokens":20761,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":3065,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012y2fFofaYqh7GoHST4TjxC","session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"9b3f85ba-f312-4fe9-ac76-0050e25eeb6e"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017B3Kr2oeCGbkS4HeEHKbji","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* Testbench: Mode Control — Slow Ramp (0.1 V/µs)\n     2→* BVDD ramp 0→10.5V at 0.1V/µs. Verify no oscillation near thresholds.\n     3→\n     4→.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n     5→.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n     6→.include \"design.cir\"\n     7→\n     8→.option method=gear reltol=1e-3 abstol=1e-12 vntol=1e-6 gmin=1e-12\n     9→.option itl1=300 itl2=200 itl4=50\n    10→\n    11→Vbvdd bvdd gnd PWL(0 0 105u 10.5)\n    12→Vpvdd pvdd gnd 5.0\n    13→Vsvdd svdd gnd 2.2\n    14→Vref  vref gnd 1.226\n    15→Ven   en_ret gnd 0\n    16→\n    17→XDUT bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off mode_control\n    18→\n    19→.tran 100n 110u uic\n    20→\n    21→.control\n    22→run\n    23→\n    24→* Measure thresholds: comp crossing 2.5V (50% of PVDD)\n    25→meas tran thresh_por FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp1) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=1u\n    26→meas tran thresh_ret FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp2) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=1u\n    27→meas tran thresh_pup FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp3) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=1u\n    28→meas tran thresh_act FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp4) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=1u\n    29→\n    30→* Check monotonicity\n    31→let mono = 1\n    32→if thresh_por >= thresh_ret\n    33→  let mono = 0\n    34→end\n    35→if thresh_ret >= thresh_pup\n    36→  let mono = 0\n    37→end\n    38→if thresh_pup >= thresh_act\n    39→  let mono = 0\n    40→end\n    41→\n    42→* All four thresholds found and monotonic = pass\n    43→let pass = mono\n    44→\n    45→echo \"thresh_por_V: $&thresh_por\"\n    46→echo \"thresh_ret_V: $&thresh_ret\"\n    47→echo \"thresh_pup_V: $&thresh_pup\"\n    48→echo \"thresh_act_V: $&thresh_act\"\n    49→echo \"monotonic: $&mono\"\n    50→echo \"works_slow_ramp: $&pass\"\n    51→\n    52→.endc\n    53→\n    54→.end\n    55→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012y2fFofaYqh7GoHST4TjxC","session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"943bcb67-4231-473d-b226-cd216430dc6f","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:55:49.400Z"}
