{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Dtx1KBrUzNPSkwhHKAecWM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Us9vUcAxVsBRcLx8uwxCxW","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/tb_mc_power_down.spice"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3065,"cache_read_input_tokens":20761,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":3065,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012y2fFofaYqh7GoHST4TjxC","session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"ce50d4e2-1998-4f76-a4d1-73fb2756e121"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Us9vUcAxVsBRcLx8uwxCxW","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* Testbench: Mode Control — Power Down (BVDD 10.5V → 0V at 1V/µs)\n     2→* Verify correct reverse mode sequence on BVDD power-down.\n     3→\n     4→.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n     5→.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n     6→.include \"design.cir\"\n     7→\n     8→.option method=gear reltol=1e-3 abstol=1e-12 vntol=1e-6 gmin=1e-12\n     9→.option itl1=300 itl2=200 itl4=50\n    10→\n    11→Vbvdd bvdd gnd PWL(0 10.5 10.5u 0)\n    12→Vpvdd pvdd gnd 5.0\n    13→Vsvdd svdd gnd 2.2\n    14→Vref  vref gnd 1.226\n    15→Ven   en_ret gnd 0\n    16→\n    17→XDUT bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off mode_control\n    18→\n    19→.tran 10n 12u uic\n    20→\n    21→.control\n    22→run\n    23→\n    24→* Measure falling thresholds (comp crossing 2.5V on fall)\n    25→meas tran thresh_act_fall FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp4) CROSS=2.5 FALL=1 TD=100n\n    26→meas tran thresh_pup_fall FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp3) CROSS=2.5 FALL=1 TD=100n\n    27→meas tran thresh_ret_fall FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp2) CROSS=2.5 FALL=1 TD=100n\n    28→meas tran thresh_por_fall FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp1) CROSS=2.5 FALL=1 TD=100n\n    29→\n    30→* Check reverse monotonicity: act > pup > ret > por (all falling)\n    31→let rev_mono = 1\n    32→if thresh_act_fall <= thresh_pup_fall\n    33→  let rev_mono = 0\n    34→end\n    35→if thresh_pup_fall <= thresh_ret_fall\n    36→  let rev_mono = 0\n    37→end\n    38→if thresh_ret_fall <= thresh_por_fall\n    39→  let rev_mono = 0\n    40→end\n    41→\n    42→echo \"thresh_act_fall_V: $&thresh_act_fall\"\n    43→echo \"thresh_pup_fall_V: $&thresh_pup_fall\"\n    44→echo \"thresh_ret_fall_V: $&thresh_ret_fall\"\n    45→echo \"thresh_por_fall_V: $&thresh_por_fall\"\n    46→echo \"reverse_monotonic: $&rev_mono\"\n    47→echo \"power_down_correct: $&rev_mono\"\n    48→\n    49→.endc\n    50→\n    51→.end\n    52→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012y2fFofaYqh7GoHST4TjxC","session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"1db2af66-daab-4fea-9b7b-a57dea18b941","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:55:49.670Z"}
