{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011xGuVg8jmEvEFGU6ARPQuc","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* Testbench: Mode Control — Hysteresis measurement\n     2→* BVDD triangle: 0→10.5V (1V/µs) then 10.5V→0 (1V/µs)\n     3→* Measures rising and falling thresholds to compute hysteresis.\n     4→\n     5→.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n     6→.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n     7→.include \"design.cir\"\n     8→\n     9→.option method=gear reltol=1e-3 abstol=1e-12 vntol=1e-6 gmin=1e-12\n    10→.option itl1=300 itl2=200 itl4=50\n    11→\n    12→Vbvdd bvdd gnd PWL(0 0 10.5u 10.5 21u 0)\n    13→Vpvdd pvdd gnd 5.0\n    14→Vsvdd svdd gnd 2.2\n    15→Vref  vref gnd 1.226\n    16→Ven   en_ret gnd 0\n    17→\n    18→XDUT bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off mode_control\n    19→\n    20→.tran 10n 22u uic\n    21→\n    22→.control\n    23→run\n    24→\n    25→* Rising thresholds\n    26→meas tran thresh_por_rise FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp1) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=100n\n    27→meas tran thresh_ret_rise FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp2) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=100n\n    28→meas tran thresh_pup_rise FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp3) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=100n\n    29→meas tran thresh_act_rise FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp4) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=100n\n    30→\n    31→* Falling thresholds (after peak at 10.5u)\n    32→meas tran thresh_act_fall FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp4) CROSS=2.5 FALL=1 TD=10.5u\n    33→meas tran thresh_pup_fall FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp3) CROSS=2.5 FALL=1 TD=10.5u\n    34→meas tran thresh_ret_fall FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp2) CROSS=2.5 FALL=1 TD=10.5u\n    35→meas tran thresh_por_fall FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp1) CROSS=2.5 FALL=1 TD=10.5u\n    36→\n    37→* Compute hysteresis (rising - falling) for each comparator\n    38→* Current design uses simple inverters, so hysteresis ~0\n    39→let hyst1 = (thresh_por_rise - thresh_por_fall) * 1000\n    40→let hyst2 = (thresh_ret_rise - thresh_ret_fall) * 1000\n    41→let hyst3 = (thresh_pup_rise - thresh_pup_fall) * 1000\n    42→let hyst4 = (thresh_act_rise - thresh_act_fall) * 1000\n    43→\n    44→* Min and max hysteresis\n    45→let hyst_min = hyst1\n    46→if hyst2 < hyst_min\n    47→  let hyst_min = hyst2\n    48→end\n    49→if hyst3 < hyst_min\n    50→  let hyst_min = hyst3\n    51→end\n    52→if hyst4 < hyst_min\n    53→  let hyst_min = hyst4\n    54→end\n    55→\n    56→let hyst_max = hyst1\n    57→if hyst2 > hyst_max\n    58→  let hyst_max = hyst2\n    59→end\n    60→if hyst3 > hyst_max\n    61→  let hyst_max = hyst3\n    62→end\n    63→if hyst4 > hyst_max\n    64→  let hyst_max = hyst4\n    65→end\n    66→\n    67→echo \"thresh_por_rise_V: $&thresh_por_rise\"\n    68→echo \"thresh_ret_rise_V: $&thresh_ret_rise\"\n    69→echo \"thresh_pup_rise_V: $&thresh_pup_rise\"\n    70→echo \"thresh_act_rise_V: $&thresh_act_rise\"\n    71→echo \"thresh_act_fall_V: $&thresh_act_fall\"\n    72→echo \"thresh_pup_fall_V: $&thresh_pup_fall\"\n    73→echo \"thresh_ret_fall_V: $&thresh_ret_fall\"\n    74→echo \"thresh_por_fall_V: $&thresh_por_fall\"\n    75→echo \"hyst_por_mV: $&hyst1\"\n    76→echo \"hyst_ret_mV: $&hyst2\"\n    77→echo \"hyst_pup_mV: $&hyst3\"\n    78→echo \"hyst_act_mV: $&hyst4\"\n    79→echo \"hysteresis_min_mV: $&hyst_min\"\n    80→echo \"hysteresis_max_mV: $&hyst_max\"\n    81→\n    82→.endc\n    83→\n    84→.end\n    85→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012y2fFofaYqh7GoHST4TjxC","session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"f8c83247-1633-4eae-acda-428eb0d32e50","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:55:50.190Z"}
