{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SXg66mbxV8R6BRoC4TWVEf","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* Testbench: Mode Control — Quiescent Current (active mode, BVDD=7V)\n     2→* Measures Iq drawn from BVDD in active mode.\n     3→\n     4→.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n     5→.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n     6→.include \"design.cir\"\n     7→\n     8→.option method=gear reltol=1e-3 abstol=1e-12 vntol=1e-6 gmin=1e-12\n     9→.option itl1=300 itl2=200 itl4=50\n    10→\n    11→Vbvdd bvdd gnd PWL(0 0 0.01u 7 1u 7)\n    12→Vpvdd pvdd gnd 5.0\n    13→Vsvdd svdd gnd 2.2\n    14→Vref  vref gnd 1.226\n    15→Ven   en_ret gnd 0\n    16→\n    17→XDUT bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off mode_control\n    18→\n    19→.tran 1n 1u uic\n    20→\n    21→.control\n    22→run\n    23→\n    24→meas tran iq_val AVG i(Vbvdd) FROM=0.5u TO=0.9u\n    25→let iq_ua = abs(iq_val) * 1e6\n    26→\n    27→echo \"iq_active_uA: $&iq_ua\"\n    28→\n    29→.endc\n    30→\n    31→.end\n    32→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012y2fFofaYqh7GoHST4TjxC","session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"be4b9405-8027-439a-94f9-b33465416145","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:55:50.799Z"}
