{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01JSfR21KbXHufBiDpU8wTQh","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* Testbench: Mode Control — PVT placeholder (TT corner only)\n     2→* Runs normal ramp at TT 27C, reports thresholds and max error.\n     3→* To be extended with SS/FF/SF/FS at -40/27/150C when corner libs available.\n     4→\n     5→.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n     6→.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n     7→.include \"design.cir\"\n     8→\n     9→.option method=gear reltol=1e-3 abstol=1e-12 vntol=1e-6 gmin=1e-12\n    10→.option itl1=300 itl2=200 itl4=50\n    11→\n    12→Vbvdd bvdd gnd PWL(0 0 10.5u 10.5)\n    13→Vpvdd pvdd gnd 5.0\n    14→Vsvdd svdd gnd 2.2\n    15→Vref  vref gnd 1.226\n    16→Ven   en_ret gnd 0\n    17→\n    18→XDUT bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off mode_control\n    19→\n    20→.tran 10n 12u uic\n    21→\n    22→.control\n    23→run\n    24→\n    25→* Measure TT 27C thresholds\n    26→meas tran thresh_por FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp1) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=500n\n    27→meas tran thresh_ret FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp2) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=500n\n    28→meas tran thresh_pup FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp3) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=500n\n    29→meas tran thresh_act FIND v(bvdd) WHEN v(xdut.comp4) CROSS=2.5 RISE=1 TD=500n\n    30→\n    31→* Calculate percent error from nominal targets\n    32→let e1 = abs(thresh_por - 2.5) / 2.5 * 100\n    33→let e2 = abs(thresh_ret - 4.2) / 4.2 * 100\n    34→let e3 = abs(thresh_pup - 4.5) / 4.5 * 100\n    35→let e4 = abs(thresh_act - 5.6) / 5.6 * 100\n    36→let max_err = e1\n    37→if e2 > max_err\n    38→  let max_err = e2\n    39→end\n    40→if e3 > max_err\n    41→  let max_err = e3\n    42→end\n    43→if e4 > max_err\n    44→  let max_err = e4\n    45→end\n    46→\n    47→echo \"corner: TT_27C\"\n    48→echo \"thresh_por_V: $&thresh_por\"\n    49→echo \"thresh_ret_V: $&thresh_ret\"\n    50→echo \"thresh_pup_V: $&thresh_pup\"\n    51→echo \"thresh_act_V: $&thresh_act\"\n    52→echo \"error_por_pct: $&e1\"\n    53→echo \"error_ret_pct: $&e2\"\n    54→echo \"error_pup_pct: $&e3\"\n    55→echo \"error_act_pct: $&e4\"\n    56→echo \"thresh_max_error_pct: $&max_err\"\n    57→\n    58→.endc\n    59→\n    60→.end\n    61→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012y2fFofaYqh7GoHST4TjxC","session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"2e9cc02b-0e65-45c0-9c7a-f4809d6a1a48","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:55:51.016Z"}
