{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CejUptiiALiTtJNzumjjaR","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* Testbench: Mode Control — Quiescent Current\n     2→.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n     3→.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n     4→.include \"design.cir\"\n     5→.option method=gear reltol=1e-3 abstol=1e-12 vntol=1e-6 gmin=1e-12\n     6→.option itl1=300 itl2=200 itl4=50\n     7→Vbvdd bvdd gnd PWL(0 0 0.1u 7 1u 7)\n     8→Vpvdd pvdd gnd 5.0\n     9→Vsvdd svdd gnd 2.2\n    10→Vref  vref gnd 1.226\n    11→Ven   en_ret gnd 0\n    12→XDUT bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off mode_control\n    13→.tran 1n 1u uic\n    14→.control\n    15→run\n    16→meas tran iq_val AVG i(vbvdd) FROM=0.5u TO=0.9u\n    17→let iq_ua = abs(iq_val) * 1e6\n    18→echo \"iq_active_uA: $&iq_ua\"\n    19→.endc\n    20→.end\n    21→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"43d75e27-5dea-4706-897b-146e33011848","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:56:51.855Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/tb_mc_iq.spice","content":"* Testbench: Mode Control — Quiescent Current\n.include \"parasitic_res_po.spice\"\n.lib \"../sky130.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"design.cir\"\n.option method=gear reltol=1e-3 abstol=1e-12 vntol=1e-6 gmin=1e-12\n.option itl1=300 itl2=200 itl4=50\nVbvdd bvdd gnd PWL(0 0 0.1u 7 1u 7)\nVpvdd pvdd gnd 5.0\nVsvdd svdd gnd 2.2\nVref  vref gnd 1.226\nVen   en_ret gnd 0\nXDUT bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off mode_control\n.tran 1n 1u uic\n.control\nrun\nmeas tran iq_val AVG i(vbvdd) FROM=0.5u TO=0.9u\nlet iq_ua = abs(iq_val) * 1e6\necho \"iq_active_uA: $&iq_ua\"\n.endc\n.end\n","numLines":21,"startLine":1,"totalLines":21}}}
