{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01AcAXaq9eYh9dbWanKxXigF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"14/16! Two failures:\n1. **thresh_por_V = 2.886** (max 2.7V) — comp1 threshold shifted when we changed second inverter from PVDD to BVDD\n2. **thresh_max_error_pct = 15.43%** (spec ≤ 15%) — mainly from the comp1 error\n\nThe BVDD-powered second inverter has a different trip point than the PVDD-powered one (because BVDD varies during the ramp). At the comp1 threshold crossing (BVDD≈2.5V), the second inverter is powered from 2.5V, not 5V, giving a different response.\n\nI need to adjust the ladder ratio for comp1 to compensate. Let me increase tap1 slightly."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":631,"cache_read_input_tokens":472108,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":631},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"1170963e-66c9-4a62-9034-792ca8d0daba"}
