{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01FvsDzDapt1gHSrT8223i3s","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/design.cir has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c97cdc95-3b2e-4d91-8a95-126c51f9e013","uuid":"f48dde15-49ff-4b65-be10-7699062b9ddf","timestamp":"2026-03-29T17:00:41.397Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/pvdd_regulator/08_mode_control/design.cir","oldString":"XRpo_pu bvdd pass_off gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=50","newString":"* Pull-up removed to save Iq. pass_off defaults correctly via PVDD logic.\n* XRpo_pu bvdd pass_off gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=50","originalFile":"* Block 08: Mode Control — v11 (vref-referenced inverter threshold)\n* PVDD 5V LDO Regulator — SkyWater SKY130A\n*\n* Each comp: PFET pull-up from PVDD + NFET with source=vref (not GND).\n* Trip at tap = vref + Vth_n ≈ 1.226 + 0.789 = 2.015V (+ body effect ~2.1V)\n* Shared ladder with ratios so tap reaches ~2.1V at each BVDD threshold.\n* Ratios boosted ~15% to compensate RC lag.\n*\n* trip ≈ 2.1V (estimated with body effect from Vsb=vref=1.226V)\n* ratio1 = 2.1/2.5*1.12 = 0.94 (boosted for RC lag)\n* ratio2 = 2.1/4.2*1.12 = 0.56\n* ratio3 = 2.1/4.5*1.12 = 0.52\n* ratio4 = 2.1/5.6*1.12 = 0.42\n*\n* R_ladder ~300kΩ total (l_tot~142µm)\n*   Rbot/Rtot = 0.42 → l=60µm\n*   R34 = 0.10 → l=14µm\n*   R23 = 0.04 → l=6µm\n*   R12 = 0.38 → l=54µm\n*   Rtop = 0.06 → l=8µm\n*\n.subckt mode_control bvdd pvdd svdd gnd vref en_ret bypass_en ea_en ref_sel uvov_en ilim_en pass_off\n\n* =============================================\n* RESISTOR LADDER (~300kΩ, ~23µA at 7V from BVDD)\n* =============================================\n* Ladder ~350kΩ (Iq ~20µA at 7V). Ratios boosted ~30% for RC lag compensation.\n* target ratios: r1=0.96, r2=0.60, r3=0.56, r4=0.45\n* Rbot=0.45*166=75, R34=0.11*166=18, R23=0.04*166=7, R12=0.36*166=60, Rtop=0.04*166=7\n* Ladder ~400kΩ (Iq ~17.5µA at 7V). Scale all by 1.14x\nXRtop bvdd tap1 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=8\nXR12  tap1 tap2 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=68\nXR23  tap2 tap3 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=8\nXR34  tap3 tap4 gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=21\nXRbot tap4 gnd  gnd sky130_fd_pr__res_xhigh_po w=1 l=86\nC_tap1 tap1 gnd 100f\nC_tap2 tap2 gnd 100f\nC_tap3 tap3 gnd 100f\nC_tap4 tap4 gnd 100f\n\n* =============================================\n* COMPARATORS: PFET from PVDD + NFET source=vref\n* Trip ≈ vref + Vth_n + body_effect ≈ 2.1V\n* =============================================\n\n* COMP1\nXMc1ivp c1inv tap1 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc1ivn c1inv tap1 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc1iv2p comp1 c1inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc1iv2n comp1 c1inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* COMP2\nXMc2ivp c2inv tap2 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc2ivn c2inv tap2 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc2iv2p comp2 c2inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc2iv2n comp2 c2inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* COMP3\nXMc3ivp c3inv tap3 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc3ivn c3inv tap3 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc3iv2p comp3 c3inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc3iv2n comp3 c3inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* COMP4\nXMc4ivp c4inv tap4 pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc4ivn c4inv tap4 gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc4iv2p comp4 c4inv pvdd pvdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_g5v0d10v5 w=40e-6 l=20e-6\nXMc4iv2n comp4 c4inv gnd  gnd  sky130_fd_pr__nfet_g5v0d10v5 w=20e-6 l=20e-6\n\n* =============================================\n* LOGIC (from BVDD)\n* =======================================